content.rendered:
Directed by Prem Mistry.

Written by Abhishek Yadav. Prem Mistry. Devanshi Shah. Talha Siddiqui. Gaganjeet Singh.

Cast  Ritvik Sahore( Abhilash 1) . Srishti Rindani( Sanya 1) . Saloni Khanna( Sushmita 1) . Abhinav Sharma( Raghav 1) . Saloni Gaur( Priyanka ) . Rajesh Yadav( Sandy ) . Gulshan Nain( Goldie ) . Manoj Joshi( Dean Amrit Sir ) . Ramandeep Yadav( Prithviraj ) . Meherzan Mazda( Nikhil ) . Ranjan Raj( Inquilab ) . Lovekush Kundu( Canteen Guy ) . Sameer Rahman( Yash ) . Chetan Raghav( Ronnie ) . Anna Ador( Chloe ) . Abhishek Yadav( College Senior ) . Sanjeev Goswami( Sports professor ) . Vikrant Singh( Bhaiya ji ) . Ritika Sharma( Tina ) . Rajani Gupta( Warden ) . Devraj Singh Rathore( Fake Nikhil ) . Mousumi Chatterjee( Sushmita’s Neighbour ) . Rajni Bajaj( Mrs. Gupta ) . Ajay Madhok( Professor Mukhopadhyay ) . Vikrant Singh( Bhaiya ji ) . Kushagre Dua( Aditya unknow)

Language Hindi.

Producers Abhishek Yadav. Sanjeev Goswami. Anand Jain. Vicky Makhu. Satish Ranjan Michael. Sumeet Mishra. Prem Mistry. Ronak Motla. Ninad Raikar. Gabbar Sangrur. Vivek Sharma. Gautam Talwar. Riddhi Wadhwa. Gautam Talwar.

Production Streamline Productions. Yellow Montage.

Creator Abhishek Yadav. Prem Mistry.

Number of Seasons 1

Number of Episodes 12

Status OnGoing (2022–)
